## ✅ Outcomes & Learnings

- Learned how to provision VNets and VMs using Azure Portal.
- Gained hands-on experience configuring **VNet Peering**.
- Understood network communication across isolated virtual networks.
- Practiced security configuration using **NSGs**.

---

## 📚 Next Steps (Future Enhancements)

- Implement custom DNS across VNets  
- Add Application Security Groups (ASG)  
- Monitor traffic using Network Watcher  
- Test cross-region VNet peering  

